7-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Mina, let's clean up before we go,\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"미나, 가기 전에 청소하고 가자,\" 준이 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-118-the-helping-hands/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"let's","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":880,"endMs":1160},{"word":"clean","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1300},{"word":"up","charStart":19,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1500},{"word":"before","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1740},{"word":"we","charStart":29,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1980},{"word":"go","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2280},{"word":"he","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2420},{"word":"said","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2680}]}]},{"id":"daily-118-the-helping-hands-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-118-the-helping-hands/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-118-the-helping-hands-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina swept the floor while Jun fixed the curtains.","translation_ko":"미나는 바닥을 쓸고 준은 커튼을 고쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-118-the-helping-hands/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"swept","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":480,"endMs":960},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":960,"endMs":1160},{"word":"floor","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1400},{"word":"while","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1840},{"word":"Jun","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2160},{"word":"fixed","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2500},{"word":"the","charStart":37,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2740},{"word":"curtains","charStart":41,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3120}]},{"id":"daily-118-the-helping-hands-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"They worked together because the room was big.","translation_ko":"방이 넓었기 때문에 둘은 힘을 합쳐 일했어요.","